    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you're the only chef in the whole restaurant and the customers step out of line, you have to STRIKE BACK! This is a game where you get to treat customers how they treat you and finally get the revenge every customer service employee deserves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chef Strikes Back</strong> is an isometric style <strong>cooking Simulator / Hack'n'Slash</strong>, where you have to cook for and feed the <strong>good customers </strong>before their patience runs out. If their patience runs out, they turn into bad customers, the bad customers will stop at nothing to ruin the restaurant in all different ways.</p>",
